<div><head>長沙耆舊傳</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1324_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1324_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1324_CHANT_001-1a.2">南陽太守張忠曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1324_CHANT_001-1a.3">「吾年往志盡，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1324_CHANT_001-1a.4">譬如八百錢馬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1324_CHANT_001-1a.5">死生同價。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1324_CHANT_001-1a.6">太尉壽少過相師，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1324_CHANT_001-1a.7">相師曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1324_CHANT_001-1a.8">「凡鼻為氣戶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1324_CHANT_001-1a.9">君鼻大貴之象。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
